<center>The High Priest Rollo
<center>continued to repent
<center>of his past sins day and night.

<center>One day <hero> all of a sudden
<center>I had a strange dream.

<center>I remember years ago
<center>when a guy first meets a girl...
<voice_0x010014D8><se_low>King of tricks: Greetings, friends from the media.
<voice_0x010014D9><se_high>*: Maharaj, here's a slap for you.
<voice_0x010014DB><se_low>King of tricks: What to do, what to do...
